 The negative CD has the following information: ZZ Top — Greatest Hits: raw, groove‑first Texas blues‑rock — concise 3–4.5‑minute riff‑driven singles, dry close‑miked gravelly vocals with breath detail, warm analogue midrange preserving muscular low‑mids, minimal remastering/low compression, punchy drums, tight rhythmic pockets and roomy stereo depth for listeners craving live immediacy.

