Why Harmony‑first singles comp best matches my preferences
- Harmony‑first and dense multitrack overdubs: The comp is explicitly “harmony‑first” with dense vocal overdubs, which directly matches my preference for inventive, communal harmonies and studio‑layered vocal productions that reward repeat listens.
